1.Config Server : Centralized configuration.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.Discovery Server (Service Registry) - 
Technology used: Spring Cloud Netflix Eureka
Purpose:

Microservices register themselves here.

Instead of calling:

http://localhost:8081/users

Services call using:

http://USER-SERVICE/users
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3.API Gateway
Purpose:
Single entry point for all requests.

Client never calls services directly.
Instead of:

client → user-service
client → project-service
client → task-service

Client calls only:

client → API Gateway

Example:
/api/users
/api/projects
/api/tasks
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
